text: Franz Stöckli was a Swiss bobsledder who competed in the early 1950s. He won two bronze medals in the four-man event at the FIBT World Championships, earning them in 1950 and 1951. ==References== *Bobsleigh four-man world championship medalists since 1930 Category:Possibly living people Category:Swiss male bobsledders Category:Year of birth missing
title: Franz Stöckli
